36:The session-recording subsystem (Spec 1) provides the substrate: `SessionRecorder` captures any `World` run; `SessionReplayer.selfCheck()` verifies replay determinism. The remaining missing piece is a *driver* — code that runs a `World` autonomously without a human at the keyboard.
